{"tid":609105,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前港姐楊婉儀遭指涉串謀詐騙，雙非幼稚園STEAM入稟求頒令還款賠償","createTime":"2018-03-28T17:27:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T07:02:52.000Z","uid":35221,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"284666af259e1136b219a24ce0617aac753c6376","tid":609105,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T17:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180328/s00001/30d69b580bab32c3121f2fa2ef7b08ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180328%2Fs00001%2F30d69b580bab32c3121f2fa2ef7b08ab.jpg&h=90b149ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - 被告楊婉儀。（明報資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n港聞<br />\n2018年3月28日 星期三 <br />\n前港姐楊婉儀遭指涉串謀詐騙　幼園入稟求頒令還款賠償 (14:59)<br />\n<br />\n前港姐楊婉儀所開辦的幼稚園，再惹官非。STEAM國際幼稚園日前入稟高院，指楊婉儀本為STEAM的董事及學校監督，惟校方於本月發現，楊婉儀自去年11月起擅自指示員工，要求學生將學費等費用，轉交其名下另一公司，涉款14.7萬。楊亦擅自將其名下公司的地址轉為STEAM校舍地址，誤導家長認為兩公司有關係。STEAM已於本月中止楊的董事資格，並指楊涉與名下公司串謀詐騙，現要求法庭頒令楊還款、賠償及交代涉款去向。<br />\n<br />\n原訴為American Schools Foundation Limited及American Education Foundation Limited。公司註冊處顯示，楊婉儀仍為兩原訴公司董事，另一董事為賴天賜。<br />\n<br />\n被告則分別為楊婉儀，及其名下的Marker Spaces Limited（前稱Golden Gate International Schools Limited）。<br />\n<br />\n原訴在入稟狀指，原訴分別在土瓜灣經營STEAM International Kindergarten（下稱STEAM），並在幼稚園內舉辦興趣班。楊婉儀為原訴的公司董事及學校監督，惟至本月14日，其董事資格及在校的職位已被中止。<br />\n<br />\n原訴指，楊婉儀自去年11月起，擅自指示學校職員，要求學生家長將學費和補習費等費用，改為交予楊婉儀及其名下公司，涉款7450元至84,084元。楊婉儀亦擅自將其名下公司地址，改為STEAM校舍地址，誤導家長以為STEAM與其名下公司有關。<br />\n<br />\n原訴指出，楊婉儀至今仍未交還上述款項，令公司造成損失。原訴認為，楊婉儀沒有避免其公司與原訴有利益衝突，更認為兩被告涉串謀詐騙。原訴另因楊婉儀違反其董事責任，本月14日中止其董事資格，及將其撤職。<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180328/s00001/1522218561103\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180328%2Fs00001%2F1522218561103&d=GRi6ROCj8D%2BfclimXTcDisKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=043fdd00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180328%2Fs00001%2F1522218561103&h=2b386fb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180328/s00001/1522218561103</a>"},{"pid":"629b7a0addf68e327d6ac5b6b7b8f0d840459fdb","tid":609105,"uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T17:28:20.000Z","msg":"舊帖討論<br />\n<br />\n楊婉儀開辦，「雙非優先」幼稚園執笠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/243430\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/243430</a>"},{"pid":"20c24756d25bea0b6cb36a0360b54d592bc879d1","tid":609105,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T17:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0130d86c50e676c84f629acf510cb766d7887a0e","tid":609105,"uid":62494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T17:36:05.000Z","msg":"突眼金魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa31d9e7ba8fe8adfdac5c348220ca7539d7288","tid":609105,"uid":550,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T18:16:50.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆當年主持六合彩40幾人中頭獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知有冇串謀詐騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa72f8184ae9028ddf6bf791196bed4d15dc8d40","tid":609105,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T04:24:05.000Z","msg":"呢張相望落幾似小坂惠"},{"pid":"a9c5f747bfced78e670bbbbe4cbc220594c1108a","tid":609105,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5fa31d9e7ba8fe8adfdac5c348220ca7539d7288","tid":609105,"uid":550,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T18:16:50.000Z","msg":"呢條八婆當年主持六合彩40幾人中頭獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知有冇串謀詐騙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018